    <string name="help_introduction">
       &lt;h1>Introduction&lt;/h1>
		Remota is an application which can be used as an air mouse and an air keyboard.
		You can remote control your host PC with simple user interfaces like a touch pad or Wii motion plus.
    </string>
    <string name="help_first_use">
        &lt;h1>For first use&lt;/h1>
        For first use, you need some preparations. Please go to the Help page.
    </string>
    <string name="help_requirements">
		&lt;h1>Requirements&lt;/h1>
		&lt;ul>
		&lt;li>A Bluetooth dongle on your host PC&lt;/li>
		&lt;li>An application on your host PC&lt;/li>
		&lt;/ul>
		
		Remota runs on the Bluetooth Serial Port Profile(SPP), so you need a Bluetooth dongle.
		Packets from your phone to your host PC go on a Bluetooth serial port as general data,
		so your host PC needs an application for analyze this data.
    </string>
    <string name="help_preparations">
		&lt;h1>Preparations&lt;/h1>
